  "texts": [
    "The values (yes/no) entered by the licensed study staff are stored in structured fields for each question.",
    "We extracted the data for the 1 inclusion and 12 exclusion criteria questions determined by the study staff's review of the medical records.",
    "During screening, study staff stop reviewing an individual patient and mark them as ineligible as soon as they meet one of the 17 exclusion criteria.",
    "Because of this process, there were missing answers for the remaining exclusion criteria.",
    "To compare RECTIFIER vs. study staff performance for screening, an expert clinician completed a blinded review of all patients and answered the questions previously answered by the study staff, thus establishing the \"gold standard\" answers."
  ],
  "correct_citations": []
}